</b></p>
<p>107. JAL 12/1/2011. Case no. EGY 1/2012. State Reply: 14/05/12. Alleged raids on 
several NGOs' offices. 
</p>
<p>108. JAL 19/1/2011. Case no. EGY 2/2012. State Reply: None to date. Alleged violence 
against women by the Egyptian military in the context of the protests that took place in 
Cairo in November and December 2011. 
</p>
<p>109. JAL 24/2/2011. Case no. EGY 5/2012. State Reply: None to date. Alleged 
increasingly restrictive environment for civil society organizations and activists. 
