</b></p>
<p>150. JUA 29/7/2011. Case no. IND 14/2011. State Reply: 03/08/2011. Alleged acts of 
violence and intimidation in the context of forced evictions. 
</p>
<p>151. JUA 5/8/2011. Case no. IND 16/2011. State Reply: 08/08/2011. Detention and 
allegations of acts of intimidation against residents of the villages located on Chhindwada. 
</p>
<p>152. JUA 9/9/2011. Case no. IND 19/2011. State Reply: 21/09/2011. Alleged killing, 
attacks and threats against women human rights defenders. 
